<br>
Covered in Dark Moon. All false. The Van Allen belts are very dasngerous. Here's a seed of NASA floating around in people's brains.<br>
<br>
-Satellites in geosyncronous orbit (like TV broadcast satellites) are inside the Van Allen Belt for their entire lifetime. Electronics can be damaged by radiation just like our bodies, but these satellites function for years without showing any effect from the radiation.<br>
<br>
Also covered in the before mentioned book. The Van Allen belts are around Earth, but far enough away so that the craft which orbited Earth would not be harmed.<br>
<br>
-You have to ask yourselves why Fox or people like Bart Sibrel tell you these lies about the moon hoax. What motivates them? Money does. Fox needs to sell advertising, which is a lot easier to do when you produce contraversial programs. Sibrel has a movie to sell and expenses to recover. They are biased sources and can not be trusted.<br>
<br>
