<br>
150 millirem (one millirem is one-one thousandth of a rem, the standard U.S. measurement for radiation) is the average annual dosage of radiation at sea level in the U.S.<br>
<br>
Short term radiation doses of 75 to 200 rem cause radiation sickness in 5%-50% of exposed individuals, with the percentage approaching 50 as the dosage approaches 200 rem. At 300 rem, radiation sickness affects anyone exposed and fatalities begin to occur. Fatalities reach 50% at 450 rem and 80% at 600 rem. Almost nobody survives a dose of 1000 rem or higher. Keep in mind this is for short term doses on the order of exposure to the flash of a nuclear detonation or to the release products of a nuclear reactor.<br>
<br>
The Apollo spacecraft only spent half an hour each way in VAB, for a total of one hour. Due to the shielding provided by the spacecraft, the one-way dosage was 4 rem to each astronaut; 8 rem round trip. While this is enough to increase the chances of developing cancer over the next 30 years (by about .1448%) it was nowhere near the amount to cause death or even radiation sickness. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/funexplainedmysteriesfrm36.showMessageRange?topicID=73.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub16.ezboard.com/funexplainedmysteriesfrm36.showPrevMessage?topicID=73.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub16.ezboard.com/funexplainedmysteriesfrm36.showNextMessage?topicID=73.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/funexplainedmysteriesfrm36.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=73.topic&index=40><img src=http://web.ukonline.co.uk/unexplained.m/images/addreply.jpeg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/funexplainedmysteriesfrm36.emailToFriend?topicID=73.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/funexplainedmysteriesfrm36.threadControl?topicID=73.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/space/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/funexplainedmysteriesfrm36.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=73.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/funexplainedmysteriesfrm36.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=73.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> 